service.tut.pori.twitterjazz

Class TwitterLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.twitterjazz.TwitterLocation

  • public class TwitterLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    A location received from Twitter.

    Conditional Elements

    • latitude
    • longitude
    • name
    Any of the conditional fields can be omitted, but at least one of the fields must be present. If latitude is given, longitude must also be given, and vice versa.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<location>
  <name>rfFuJBaVIUpNmHNjKWaGciOKSnTxLNjaYhwdYMsWswZuQGIFhZOVQcdfsccradSm</name>
  <latitude>-87.0</latitude>
  <longitude>102.0</longitude>
</location>
